What makes our server special is that IV is so far ahead of everyone else. With all respect of PO, I dont think you really understand the different IV and PO. Being 120 lvl 55+ dosnt bring you close to dealing with Cazic Thule. Endless, Sacret Fires , Prometian Order, Agony are all making good progress especially interesting is Sacret Fires being on dragon faction and doing well in halls of testing, but IV is still beyond reach both in levels, devotion and tactics.<br>
